{"type":"message","id":"f6b03b87","parentId":"de10c9b8","timestamp":"2026-04-02T05:06:15.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've successfully:\n1. Checked sessions_list - no active user conversations in the last 5 minutes\n2. Searched for latest industry trends in enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, IT operations services, and network system integration\n3. Compiled 4 key information areas and saved them to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nThe task is complete.","thinkingSignature":"2541c35059af84de695f088efc0e1df3775f231748f5a2f50ace7cbf3d26c1b6"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 自主学习完成\n\n**执行情况**：\n- ✅ 检测到空闲（无活跃对话）\n- ✅ 搜索了4个维度的行业动态\n- ✅ 整理关键信息5条\n- ✅ 已保存至 `memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**整理的关键信息摘要**：\n\n| 领域 | 核心要点 |\n|------|---------|\n| 企业数字化转型 | 200亿专项资金、30%购置补贴、规上工业攻坚 |\n| 智能安防 | AI大模型+边缘智能、3500亿美元全球市场、民用黄金三年 |\n| IT运维服务 | AIOps 3.0自治运维、ESG绿色运维、国产化替代加速 |\n| 网络系统集成 | 智能集成平台成主流、连接+算力双轮驱动、政务一张网 |\n\n**对道简的参考价值**：赛道整体向好，需重点关注AI能力升级、平台化集成能力建设、安全合规底线能力。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5685,"output":280,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49946,"cost":{"input":0.0017055,"output":0.000336,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00336093}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775106366556}}
